<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">燉煌出土三階教殘卷</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">教籍</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">對根起行法</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
